Package net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.postprocess

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChainedResourceBundlePostProcessor
    Interface for chained bundle postprocessors, which will perform different kinds of processing on joined resource bundles, such as compression.
    ResourceBundlePostProcessor
    Interface for bundle postprocessors, which will perform different kinds of processing on joined resource bundles, such as compression.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractChainedResourceBundlePostProcessor
    Chained abstract implementation of ResourceBundlePostProcessor.
    BundleProcessingStatus
    This class encapsulates the status of a bundling process.
    EmptyResourceBundlePostProcessor
    Empty implementation of a bundle processor, which actually does nothing to a bundle.
    PostProcessFactoryConstant
    This class defines the constants for the post processors.
